description:
&lt;p&gt;We are recruiting to our Royal Stoke Elective Orthopaedic surgical ward. This is a 28 bedded unit which delivers a service to patients requiring orthopaedic surgery. Nursing staff work alongside Consultants and therapists to achieve excellence in care and to provide a positive patient experience. If you are a Registered Nurse who enjoys a fast paced surgical ward then this speciality is for you. Training and education will be provided to assist you if you are not experienced in elective orthopaedics and all newly qualified nurses will undergo a thorough perceptorship package.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are interested please contact SNR Sister Sally Keay on sally.keay@uhnm.nhs.uk&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;We look forward to your application.&lt;/p&gt;
